OL,3,CArrest made after alleged attempted
OL,4,Cabduction young woman in Cardiff suburb
OL,6,FA man has been arrested following what
OL,7,Fpolice are treating as an attempted
OL,8,Fabduction of a young woman in Cardiff.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police said the incident
OL,11,Foccurred in the Pontrennau area of
OL,12,FCardiff on Saturday, February 28th.
OL,14,FPolice say an 18 year old woman was
OL,15,Ffollowed after she got off a bus,
OL,16,Fbefore a motorist intervened.
