OL,3,CArrest made after alleged attempted
OL,4,Cabduction young woman in Cardiff suburb
OL,6,FIn a statement South Wales Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "A man has been arrested
OL,8,Ffollowing what is being treated as an
OL,9,Fattempted abduction of a 18-year-old
OL,10,Fwoman in Pontrennau area of Cardiff on
OL,11,FSaturday, February 28.
OL,13,F"A local man, 33, was arrested within
OL,14,Fhours of the incident being reported
OL,15,Fand remains in police custody".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
