OL,3,CArrest made after alleged attempted
OL,4,Cabduction young woman in Cardiff suburb
OL,6,FThe incident happened at around 6.30pm
OL,7,Fon the junction of Clos Nant Mwlan and
OL,8,FHeol Pontprennau. Police say the 18-
OL,9,Fyear-old victim got off a bus before
OL,10,Fshe is believed to have been followed
OL,11,Fby somebody on foot.
OL,13,FDetectives investigating the incident
OL,14,Fare trying to identify a woman
OL,15,Fmotorist driving a black car who saw
OL,16,Fthe incident and stopped to intervene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
