OL,3,CArrest made after alleged attempted
OL,4,Cabduction young woman in Cardiff suburb
OL,6,F"Detective Inspector Laura Parsons,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Incidents such as this one are
OL,8,Fextremely rare and I would like to
OL,9,Freassure people that we have arrested
OL,10,Fa suspect who is in police custody.
OL,12,F"'I would like to praise the woman who
OL,13,Fstopped her car to intervene. It's
OL,14,Freally important that we identify who
OL,15,Fshe is so she is urged to get in
OL,16,Ftouch".
